properties.name: Denise Robinson
properties.desc: Denise Robinson is a minor character in Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas. She is Carl Johnson's first girlfriend in the events of the game.

properties.name: Millie Perkins
properties.desc: Millie Perkins is a supporting character in Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas, and is one possible of the six girlfriends of Carl Johnson.

properties.name: Helena Wankstein
properties.desc: Helena Wankstein is a minor character in Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas and one of the girlfriends Carl Johnson can date.

properties.name: Katie Zhan
properties.desc: Katie Zhan is a minor character in Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas. She is one of Carl Johnson's optional girlfriends.

properties.name: Michelle Cannes
properties.desc: Michelle Cannes is a character who appears as a minor character in Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas. She is one of six girlfriends that Carl can engage a relationship with.

properties.name: Barbara Schternvart
properties.desc: Barbara Schternvart is a character in the Grand Theft Auto series who appears as a minor character in Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas. She can become one of Carl's potential girlfriends.
